Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.92,0:01:07.55,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}就算谁都不曾见过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.55,0:01:11.13,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}美丽的东西就是美丽的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.13,0:01:13.55,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur6}我早已知晓
